images.title: Fortress of solitude
images.caption: Füzér Castle in the Zemplén Mountains, Hungary
images.desc: Hungary is a country blessed with stunning landscapes and a host of historic castles. From the opulent Buda Castle in Budapest, with its commanding views of the Danube, to Eger Castle, renowned for its heroic defense against the Turks, each site has a story to tell.
